
OCaml Magic                                               -*-outline-*-
                                           
* What is OCaml magic

It is a binding to libmagic tries to classify files using various
tests (filesystem tests, magic number tests, and language tests).


* Installation

See the file INSTALL.


* Latest version

See http://math.umh.ac.be/an/software.php
and https://sourceforge.net/projects/ocaml-magic


